soap.local.entity

Class DBConsistencyCheckResult

  • soap.local.entity.SOAPBaseType
    • soap.local.entity.DBConsistencyCheckResult

  • public class DBConsistencyCheckResult
extends SOAPBaseType
    Class containing information resulting from the running of database consistency checks.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      int CheckType
      Type of consistency check
      String ConsistencyCheckDescription
      Get the description of the consistency check
      long Duration
      The length of time (in seconds) the check took
      String FailureDescription
      Get the description of the failure
      boolean GetNumInconsistenciesValid
      boolean GetSqlStringValid
      Is the getSqlString() method valid for the associated consistency check type.
      int NumInconsistencies
      Get the number of inconsistencies found for the check.

      This method is only valid for the following types of checks (NO_MATCH_ROWS). Call isGetNumInconsistenciesValid() first.
      String QueryToIdentifyRows
      Get the sql query to identify individual rows that failed the consistency check.

      This method is only valid for the following types of checks (NO_MATCH_ROWS). Call isGetSqlStringValid() first.
      String SqlString
      Get the sql query that was executed for the consistency check.

      This method is only valid for the following types of checks (NO_MATCH_ROWS). Call isGetSqlStringValid() first.
      boolean Succeeded
      Whether or not check succeeded
